rbeitsheft den Studierenden einen vielschichtigen, kontrastiven Einblick in Struktur und Entstehungsgeschichte beider Sprachen.  aThis book presents an in-depth comparison of two Romance languages. The authors analyze Spanish and Portuguese at every linguistic level – phonology, morphology, syntax, lexicon –, placing a special focus on their historical development, their varieties, and their global prevalence.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aContrastive linguistics. 0aPortuguese languagexGrammar, ComparativexSpanish. 0aSpanish languagexGrammar, ComparativexPortuguese. 4aKontrastive Linguistik. 4aSprachgeschichte. 4aSprachvergleich. 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / Spanish.2bisacsh  aComparative linguistics.  aContrastive linguistics.  aLanguage history.1 aGarcía Jiménez, Inma.1 aMeisnitzer, Benjamin.1 aSchöntag, Roger, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2012z9783110288896oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311025381840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311027386140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110273861423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110273861/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014